LAW ENFORCEMENT AGENCIES, AND COMMERCIAL ENTERPRISES. THE CONSIDERATION PAID IN THE PRECEDING TABLE INCLUDES $248 MILLION RELATED TO THE DECEMBER 2010 ACQUISITION OF THE REMAINING NONCONTROLLING INTEREST IN COGENT, INC. NET ASSETS ACQUIRED IN THE COGENT INC. TRANSACTION INCLUDED $532 MILLION OF CASH AND MARKETABLE SECURITIES, AS DISPLAYED IN THE PRECEDING TABLE.

